<paragraph blockId="212.[98,1274,513,637]" box="[99,1012,577,598]" pageId="212" pageNumber="817">French: Nésokia de Bunni / German: Rote Pestratte / Spanish: Rata bandicut de cola larga</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="212.[98,1274,513,637]" box="[98,1274,616,637]" pageId="212" pageNumber="817">Other common names: Bunn's Bandicoot Rat, Bunn's Short-tailed Bandicoot Rat, Long-tailed Nesokia, Red Pest Rat</paragraph>
